IMPACT\
Given the final objectives of this project it is likely that we may never truly know how much of an impact it will have on our target audience.  Especially as identifying them would require some questionable advances on players privacy.  However, no matter the impact it may have on it's own, any recognition from the Games for Change Festival would, no doubt, increase that impact and help us in furthering the objectives of Synergy.\
