\cf2 =========================================================================\
\
Synergy started as a single idea that popped into the head of Hadi Mehrpouya.  Along with Douglas Kelly and Iain J McCallum the idea was developed into a roughly thought out game design.  Due to lack of time Hadi could not continue, from this point Iain and Douglas began building, refining, re-designing and re-building the game over evenings and weekends for nearly a year.  Then Anastasia Devana stumbled across the project online, got in contact, and joined the team to create some much needed music and sound effects.  We are now nearly another year down the road and Synergy is rounding the final corner to completion.  It has been a labour of love with no funding save the donation of each members spare time and knowledge.  We hope you like playing it as much as we have enjoyed making it.\
